Mon Aug 26 00:51:16 UTC 2002  Aaron Krowne <akrowne@vt.edu> Note 0085

  1. New, improved mathytitle implementation.  This one is built around a 
     generic math-chunk rendering architecture, and a hash table of image
     binaries in the database.  New mathytitle images generated on demand.

  2. Fixed a problem with TeX->UTF8 ichar conversion by making a new TeXtoUTF8
     which does NOT convert the entire string to latin1 (only the TeX ichars.)
     For the old functionality, TeXtoUTF8_fromLatin1 should be used.

