Wed Aug 21 10:31:46 UTC 2002  Aaron Krowne <akrowne@vt.edu> Note 0082

  1. XSLified encyclopedia add/edit forms.

  2. Made considerable changes to the XSLTemplate engine.  Added some key stuff
     to make it more compatible with plain html Templates and how we were 
