Wed Jul 10 01:48:22 UTC 2002  Aaron Krowne <akrowne@vt.edu> Note 0074

  1. Changed the main operation dispatch method in PlanetMath from a (shameful)
     practice of chaining together a bunch of string comparisons with "elsifs" 
     to a hash-based lookup with the op name as key.  Not that I see any speed 
     increase (though there should be one in principle), but this is just a 
     better way to do things.

