     extended title and canonical name field to 255 characters from 128.

     Since PG doesn't have a column drop, I had to create a temporary table
     with the updated schema, then INSERT INTO SELECT ... FROM the old table.
     Then I issued a rename (ALTER TABLE ... RENAME TO ...) and re-created
     the indices.

Thu Jun  6 02:31:55 UTC 2002  Aaron Krowne <akrowne@vt.edu> Note 0061

