     bug 21.

Tue Feb 26 05:01:08 UTC 2002  Logan Hanks <logan@vt.edu> Note 0005

  1. Increased main_memory in /etc/texmf/texmf.cnf by a factor of 10.  For
     some reason using curved lines in this particular xypic figure required
     more memory.  Why this was not a problem with my automata diagrams, I do
     not know.  Note that to change texmf.cnf, after you save the file, you
     must run fmtutil --all for changes to take effect.

