     form can now set the requested request as the default item in the
     request select box if specified, and this new update link takes
     advantage of that.  The request selectbox is now generated by
     getSelectBoxSortByValue as well.

  6. Added humanReadableCmp, which is meant to define a more human readable
     ordering on strings.  Currently it is crude -- strings with
     non-alphabetic leading characters sort ahead of anything else, and
     the rest is simply a case-insensitive lexicographic sort.  It also
     strips things like quotes first, and collapses spaces.

